---
import BaseLayout from "@/layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
import { Icon } from "astro-icon/components";
import MainCard from "@/components/MainCard.astro";

---

<BaseLayout title="About">
  <MainCard

  >
    <div class="space-y-10 mb-8">
      <!-- Profile Section -->
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-6 flex items-center gap-2">
        <Icon name="lucide:user" class="w-6 h-6 text-primary" />
        <span>About Me</span>
      </h2>
      <section class="flex flex-col md:flex-row gap-8 items-center md:items-start">
        <div class="avatar">
          <div
            class="w-32 h-32 md:w-40 md:h-40 rounded-xl ring ring-primary ring-offset-base-100 ring-offset-2 overflow-hidden"
          >
            <img src="/goat.jpg" alt="XZ" width="60" height="60" loading="eager" />
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="flex-1 text-center md:text-left">
          <h1 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold mb-2">少阳</h1>
          <p class="text-xl text-base-content/80 mb-4">90后 分享生活 | 美学 摄影 文化 | 学习 思维 小众</p>

          <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-3 justify-center md:justify-start mb-6">
            <a
              href="https://github.com/zayck"
              target="_blank"
              rel="noopener noreferrer"
              class="btn btn-sm btn-outline gap-2"
            >
              <Icon name="lucide:github" class="w-4 h-4" />
              <span>GitHub</span>
            </a>
            <a
              href="https://mp.weixin.qq.com/mp/homepage?__biz=MzU2MTI5MzE4OA==&hid=1&sn=356f3016aeac48fc034804fca1307349&scene=18#wechat_redirect"
              target="_blank"
              rel="noopener noreferrer"
              class="btn btn-sm btn-outline gap-2"
            >
              <Icon name="lucide:message-circle" class="w-4 h-4" />
              <span>wechat</span>
            </a>
            <a
              href="https://space.bilibili.com/341981702"
              target="_blank"
              rel="noopener noreferrer"
              class="btn btn-sm btn-outline gap-2"
            >
              <Icon name="lucide:youtube" class="w-5 h-5" />
              <span>bilibili</span>
            </a>
          </div>
        </div>
    </div>


      <!-- 使用prose类来美化Markdown样式 -->
<div class="prose max-w-none">
  
  <div class="w-full h-px bg-gray-300"></div>
  
  <h2>😜 关于我</h2>
  
  <p>你好！我是 Zayck 少阳，一个科技树越点越歪的个人博主。</p>

  <p>90后 分享生活 | 美学 摄影 文化 | 学习 思维 小众</p>
  
  <p>公众号: <a href="https://mp.weixin.qq.com/mp/homepage?__biz=MzU2MTI5MzE4OA==&hid=1&sn=356f3016aeac48fc034804fca1307349&scene=18#wechat_redirect" class="text-blue-500 hover:text-blue-700 hover:underline transition-colors">少阳手记</a>、<a href="http://mp.weixin.qq.com/mp/homepage?__biz=MzkwNDQxODAwNA==&hid=1&sn=dba09d5d905d80eb8c71d36cb9f340ee&scene=18#wechat_redirect" class="text-blue-500 hover:text-blue-700 hover:underline transition-colors">少阳研究所</a></p>
  
  <h2>🛠️ 关于本站</h2>
  
  <p>这个网站使用 <strong>Astro</strong> 框架构建，在 <a href="https://github.com/xz131714/RyuChan" class="text-blue-500 hover:text-blue-700 hover:underline transition-colors">RyuChan</a> 主题上进行修改。之前也折腾过其他博客主题，比如：Hugo、Hexo……但还是想再折腾一下 Astro。因为这个主题的卡片风格很戳我，简洁又美观，符合我的审美要求，一下子就喜欢上了！</p>
  
  <p><strong>其他博客展示————</strong></p>

  <ul>
    <li><strong>🖥️ Hexo 博客演示：</strong> <a href="https://zayck.github.io" class="text-blue-500 hover:text-blue-700 hover:underline transition-colors">Hexo - Demo site1</a> | <a href="https://zayck.netlify.app" class="text-blue-500 hover:text-blue-700 hover:underline transition-colors">Hexo - Demo site2</a></li>
    <li><strong>🖥️ Hugo 博客演示 ：</strong> <a href="https://zayck-teek.pages.dev" class="text-blue-500 hover:text-blue-700 hover:underline transition-colors">Hugo - Demo site</a></li>
    <li><strong>🖥️ Astro Firefly演示：</strong> <a href="https://zayck-firefly.pages.dev" class="text-blue-500 hover:text-blue-700 hover:underline transition-colors">Firefly</a></li>
  </ul>  
  
  <h2>📫 联系方式</h2>
  
  <p>如果你想和我交流技术问题，分享有趣的想法，或者只是想打个招呼，欢迎通过以下方式联系我：</p>
  
  <ul>
    <li><strong>⛩️ Bilibili: </strong> <a href="https://space.bilibili.com/341981702" class="text-blue-500 hover:text-blue-700 hover:underline transition-colors">Zayck-少阳</a></li>
    <li><strong>⚜️ 微信公众号: </strong> <a href="https://mp.weixin.qq.com/mp/homepage?__biz=MzU2MTI5MzE4OA==&hid=1&sn=356f3016aeac48fc034804fca1307349&scene=18#wechat_redirect" class="text-blue-500 hover:text-blue-700 hover:underline transition-colors">少阳手记</a></li>
    <li><strong>🕋 微信公众号: </strong> <a href="https://mp.weixin.qq.com/mp/homepage?__biz=MzkwNDQxODAwNA==&hid=1&sn=dba09d5d905d80eb8c71d36cb9f340ee&scene=18#wechat_redirect" class="text-blue-500 hover:text-blue-700 hover:underline transition-colors">少阳研究所</a></li>
  </ul>
  
  <h2>💗 支持博主</h2>

  <p>感谢你的来访！希望在这里能找到对你有用的内容！如果你觉得本站内容对你有帮助，欢迎支持我的创作！你的支持是我持续更新的动力。</p>
  
<div class="mt-8 text-center">
  <button 
    id="about_donate_button"
    class="inline-block px-6 py-3 bg-amber-500 hover:bg-amber-600 text-white font-bold rounded-md shadow-md transition-colors duration-300"
    onmouseenter="donate_modal.showModal()"
  >
    支持一下
  </button>
</div>

<!-- Donate Modal -->  
<dialog id="donate_modal" class="modal modal-bottom sm:modal-middle">
  <div class="modal-box max-w-md rounded-none sm:rounded-xl p-4">
    <h3 class="font-bold text-lg sm:text-xl mb-2 text-center">
      🎉 感谢你的支持！
    </h3>
    <!-- 这里放置打赏图片，您需要替换为实际的图片路径 -->
    <div class="flex justify-center mb-0">
      <img src="/donate.webp" alt="打赏二维码" class="max-w-[90%] max-h-[250px] h-auto rounded-lg object-contain" />
    </div>
    <div class="modal-action mt-2">
      <form method="dialog">
        <button class="btn btn-ghost hover:scale-105 transition-transform">
          关闭
        </button>
      </form>
    </div>
  </div>
  <form method="dialog" class="modal-backdrop">
    <button>关闭</button>
  </form>
</dialog>

</div>

  </MainCard>
</BaseLayout>
